{
  "stem": "26142.12",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It takes a couple of weeks to-- but I didn't wait completely two weeks till when I came-- when I came for the first time back to see my sister-in-law, my brother's [NON-ENGLISH] wife, [NON-ENGLISH] was her name, she started to cry when she saw-- when she saw me first, when I told her what happened.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, this was my experience with becoming a Hungarian citizen again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That was in November.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In January or February, 1943 [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] we got a note from my mother-- my brother [NON-ENGLISH] who was the [INAUDIBLE], that my father is very sick.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother is taking him to the city of [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Khost, ?] because in [NON-ENGLISH] there was-- was a couple doctors, but just emergency rooms, but no hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To a doctor by the name of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He is coughing badly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she's taking him to the doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she kind of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sensed something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she said that we should come-- we should come to the city of [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Khost ?] and see what's-- what-- so sometimes in January, 1943, we came to the city of [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Khost. ?] And that didn't go-- didn't go so easy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We got off-- we got off the train station, we got stopped, rounded up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My brother [NON-ENGLISH] was in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And only the three of us, [NON-ENGLISH], and I went in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They rounded us up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they took us into a barracks in the city of [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Khost ?] already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But, fortunately, we had-- we had the papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were rounded up for-- held back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they checked out the papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, what are you all doing here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We told them the truth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our father is here for medical care.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
